==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[bird]]s [[of]] [[a]] [[feather]] [[flock]] [[together]]'''

# {{idiom}} People of similar [[character]], [[background]] or [[taste]] tend to [[congregate]] or [[associate]] with one another,

===Usage notes===
Birds of a fetaher flock together means that people with the same background are usually the ones who are around with one another.<!--Hmmm?-->

